title: Jaden Smith | Sal Vulcano & Chris Distefano Present: Hey Babe! | EP 87
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!
This week the babes go FULL ZADDY! What exactly is a Zaddy? Zaddy vs Dilf. Who do we think the hottest zaddies are? Clueless is a classic movie. Paul Rudd is the best! What is the most watched movie of all time. Subway has a crazy new promotion if you get a subway tattoo on your chest or back. Subway is OUT OF CONTROL! Chris goes to the beach and things go SOUTH. Chris connects with new friends on Staten Island. What's the worst job in nyc? Sal has a nightmare show on the road. Kid Cudi gets things thrown at him on stage at Rolling Loud music festival. Chris needs to get a new car! Chris meets Riff Raff......HEY BABE!
